        Student Constructor which accepts strings for a first and last name, id, and email. The parameters are also checked for blank information and the email string is checked for an "@" symbol.
        Parameters:
        firstName - First name string of the student
        lastName - Last name string of the student
        id - Student's identification number string
        email - Student's email address string
